    "about": "I'm a seasoned designer with over 15 years of experience, currently based in Stockholm. Years ago I started as a freelance designer, worked on branding, print, and web projects. Then worked across several digital agencies, but over time I dived more and more into product design and design systems.\n\nAlongside that, I'm building GETDONE, a GTD-based task planner app, we co-founded with my friend.\n\nI believe in honest and purposeful design. With that in mind, I aim to create useful, accessible, simple, and clean solutions, always searching for the balance between aesthetics and function.\n\nI'm always in learning, whether it's a new language, pushing up coding skills, or playing chess.\n\nAlso, I'm especially interested in atomic design, code as a design tool, design systems, privacy-conscious and ethical digital products, online privacy, and place for technology in our life.",
